  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438820/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765011800\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438820/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765011800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438820/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765011800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hyper Box - A real challange</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438820/extras/10759053d86205d94fd1337a1b6257c0.avif?t=1765011800\" width=466 height=180 /></span><br>Hyper Box is a challanging platformer with simple mechanics that you can use in different ways to complete the games levels.<br><br>The game contains unlockable skins and levels. A lot more will be added during the games current development.<br><br>Can you beat Hyper Box?<br><br><br>If you notice any launcher trouble during the first launch day, please notify me and it should be fixed within a couple days.<br>If this happens it will probably be a minor problem with the Steam launch option, if so you can just manually start the game from the games folder until fixed.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hyper Box - A real challange</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438820/extras/10759053d86205d94fd1337a1b6257c0.avif?t=1765011800\" width=466 height=180 /></span><br>Hyper Box is a challanging platformer with simple mechanics that you can use in different ways to complete the games levels.<br><br>The game contains unlockable skins and levels. A lot more will be added during the games current development.<br><br>Can you beat Hyper Box?<br><br><br>If you notice any launcher trouble during the first launch day, please notify me and it should be fixed within a couple days.<br>If this happens it will probably be a minor problem with the Steam launch option, if so you can just manually start the game from the games folder until fixed.",
